  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK280">
<l>maḻittalum nīṭṭalum vēṇṭā vulakam</l>
<l>paḻitta toḻittu viṭiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no need of a shaven crown, nor of tangled hair, if a man abstain from those deeds which the wise have condemned.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
